message: Hello Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product. After careful consideration, I believe it would be beneficial for both of us if we could come to an agreement. I am proposing a price of $1,350,000 for the product.
Alice, thanks for the offer. I see the value in your product, but that price is a little high for me. Could you consider $1,050,000?
Thank you for your response, Bob. I appreciate your interest in our product. Considering your feedback, I am willing to negotiate further. My counteroffer is $1,200,000 for the product.
